{"id":34191,"date":"2024-01-13T14:36:43","date_gmt":"2022-05-13T09:06:43","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=34191"},"modified":"2023-09-15T18:57:34","modified_gmt":"2023-09-15T13:27:34","slug":"black-wardrobe-design-ideas","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/black-wardrobe-design-ideas\/","title":{"rendered":"Black Wardrobe Magic: 7 Ideas For Every Kind Of Bedroom"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>They don\u2019t say stunning black for no reason. You\u2019ll love these black wardrobe ideas for your bedroom.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>We know black magic has a negative connotation to it. But a splendid black wardrobe always leaves us at a loss of words! Firstly, it\u2019s a gorgeous shade. Then the design with space optimisation makes it nothing short of a magic trick. Hence, our version of <em>black magic<\/em>. So, here are seven black wardrobe designs of varying sizes and styles for all types of bedrooms. You can rest assured that you\u2019ll find one that works best for your home set-up or renovation. Are you ready for Mission Modern Black Wardrobe? Let\u2019s get started.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">The LBD Of The Black Wardrobe World<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>When in (fashion) doubt, women always opt for the chic LBD in their closet. A black, two-door sliding<strong> <\/strong>wardrobe with an attached dresser unit is the LBD of wardrobes. It simply can\u2019t let you down, especially when it\u2019s a modular, floor-to-ceiling wardrobe. The attached dressing unit makes it further enticing besides saving crucial room space. Multiple shelves inside the wardrobe, overhead cabinets and drawers below the dressing mirror allow for efficient organisation and closet storage. This <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/types-of-wardrobe\/\">type of wardrobe<\/a> is especially ideal for a compact bedroom.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/08181055\/lbd-of-the-black-wardrobe-for-bedroom.jpg\" alt=\"Sliding two-doors black wardrobe with an attached dresser unit is the LBD of wardrobes\" class=\"wp-image-34195\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/08181055\/lbd-of-the-black-wardrobe-for-bedroom.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/08181055\/lbd-of-the-black-wardrobe-for-bedroom-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/08181055\/lbd-of-the-black-wardrobe-for-bedroom-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/08181055\/lbd-of-the-black-wardrobe-for-bedroom-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Go the LBW way for compact bedrooms<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Multi-functional Black And White Wardrobe Design<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A wardrobe that functions as cupboard space, an open bookshelf and a workstation is every urban homeowner\u2019s dream come true. This multi-functional black and white wardrobe is one of our favourites \u2014 such elegance, such utility. Isn&#8217;t the pull-out study table an unmistakable delight? Imagine this <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/space-saving-wardrobes-for-small-rooms\/\">wardrobe in a small bedroom<\/a> that occasionally converts into a guest room. The wardrobe saves the need for separate pieces of furniture for each function and is perfect for your everyday use. It gets better when there\u2019s a guest who can\u2019t stop gushing about the design.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/08181053\/multifunctional-black-and-white-wardrobe.jpg\" alt=\"A multifunctional black and white wardrobe design with a pull-out study table is ideal for a small bedroom\" class=\"wp-image-34196\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/08181053\/multifunctional-black-and-white-wardrobe.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/08181053\/multifunctional-black-and-white-wardrobe-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/08181053\/multifunctional-black-and-white-wardrobe-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/08181053\/multifunctional-black-and-white-wardrobe-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A space-saving functional black and white wardrobe<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Jazz up your bedroom with these trending wardrobe designs\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/16103214\/bedroom-with-trending-wardrobe-designs.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">An Elegant Black Tinted Glass Wardrobe<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A luxurious two-door black tinted glass wardrobe makes an opulent and bold statement. With shelves and drawers aplenty, this freestanding black glass wardrobe makes neat organisation easier. Here\u2019s another interesting aspect of the design \u2014 the clear glass ensures that you have no trouble finding your clothes and accessories in a black wardrobe. We guarantee that it steals the spotlight with its mere presence. As it\u2019s freestanding and small, you may even use it as a corner wardrobe in a smaller room.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/08181100\/black-tinted-glass-wardrobe.jpg\" alt=\"A bedroom with a black tinted glass wardrobe makes an opulent and bold statement\" class=\"wp-image-34193\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/08181100\/black-tinted-glass-wardrobe.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/08181100\/black-tinted-glass-wardrobe-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/08181100\/black-tinted-glass-wardrobe-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/08181100\/black-tinted-glass-wardrobe-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A black glass wardrobe meant for the limelight<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Sleek And Spacious Black Tinted Glass Wardrobe<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If a clear glass wardrobe doesn&#8217;t cut it for you, explore the tinted glass variant. For instance, in this <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/luxury-bedroom-interior-design-ideas\/\">luxurious bedroom<\/a>, we built a black wardrobe into the wall and gave it tinted doors. Ample hanging rods and shelves optimise the wardrobe\u2019s utility. The black wardrobe design uses a full wall (well, almost), thus allowing more space for movement in the room. More importantly, the wall use ensures that this design is feasible and customisable in bedrooms of any size.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/08181052\/sleek-and-spacious-black-tinted-glass-wardrobe.jpg\" alt=\"Luxurious bedroom's sleek and spacious black tinted glass wardrobe looks modern\" class=\"wp-image-34197\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/08181052\/sleek-and-spacious-black-tinted-glass-wardrobe.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/08181052\/sleek-and-spacious-black-tinted-glass-wardrobe-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/08181052\/sleek-and-spacious-black-tinted-glass-wardrobe-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/08181052\/sleek-and-spacious-black-tinted-glass-wardrobe-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A modern black closet with tinted glass doors<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Fashionably Wide Black Sliding Wardrobe<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A wide sliding wardrobe is a piece of accent furniture. Double that with elegant black and the accolades will just keep pouring for your excellent choice. In this bedroom, we\u2019ve used a two-door design. But we can increase the doors based on the wardrobe width you require and its storage layout. With a workstation just by its side, changing looks between virtual meetings is so easy! This design is a <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/walk-in-wardrobe-design-ideas\/\">walk-in wardrobe<\/a> in a large bedroom. Yet it can be customised to your room\u2019s dimensions.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/08181048\/wide-black-sliding-wardrobe-for-bedroom.jpg\" alt=\"A wide black sliding wardrobe in a two-door design in a large bedroom enhances the elegance\" class=\"wp-image-34199\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/08181048\/wide-black-sliding-wardrobe-for-bedroom.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/08181048\/wide-black-sliding-wardrobe-for-bedroom-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/08181048\/wide-black-sliding-wardrobe-for-bedroom-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/08181048\/wide-black-sliding-wardrobe-for-bedroom-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Black sliding wardrobe to slide in and out in style<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Also, check out <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/sliding-wardrobe-design-ideas\/\">Sliding Wardrobe Design Ideas<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Modest And Stylish Mirrored Wardrobe In Black<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A wardrobe with mirrors solves many problems in terms of space and utility. Look at our charcoal black mirrored wardrobe. This floor-to-ceiling wardrobe is sleek with four doors and can fit in any space. The dual mirrors add to its aesthetic value in addition to serving their function. It\u2019s a great choice if you want a no-fuss, maximum utility wardrobe in black.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/08181050\/stylish-mirrored-wardrobe-in-black.jpg\" alt=\"Black wardrobe design with stylish mirrored attached to doors is an excellent choice if you want a no-fuss\" class=\"wp-image-34198\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/08181050\/stylish-mirrored-wardrobe-in-black.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/08181050\/stylish-mirrored-wardrobe-in-black-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/08181050\/stylish-mirrored-wardrobe-in-black-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/08181050\/stylish-mirrored-wardrobe-in-black-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A black mirrored wardrobe that\u2019s modest yet stylish<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Get a Free Modular Kitchen Worth \u20b92 Lakhs with Your Home Interiors.\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/08183703\/designcafe-offer-free-modular-kitchen-worth-2-lakhs.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Angular Modern Black Wardrobe<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A wide wardrobe can shrink your compact bedroom further. Enter modular corner and angular wardrobes! This wardrobe design is an optimised angular black wardrobe with plenty of storage racks in varying heights and widths. This custom design makes good use of the wall space on two walls \u2014 ensuring optimal utility. A black corner wardrobe is still an efficient alternative to the angular wardrobe. We\u2019d recommend angular or corner wardrobes when you need a large, functional wardrobe to be accommodated in a compact bedroom.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/08181102\/angular-modern-black-wardrobe-for-bedroom.jpg\" alt=\"An angular modern black wardrobe with plenty of storage racks is an optimized design\" class=\"wp-image-34192\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/08181102\/angular-modern-black-wardrobe-for-bedroom.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/08181102\/angular-modern-black-wardrobe-for-bedroom-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/08181102\/angular-modern-black-wardrobe-for-bedroom-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/08181102\/angular-modern-black-wardrobe-for-bedroom-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Angular wardrobes work best in compact rooms<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Did you enjoy our handpicked selection of black wardrobe designs? Fancy setting up your bedroom with one of these designs yet? If you\u2019re ready, the next step is simple. <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/contact-us\/\">Book your appointment here<\/a> and meet our designers. Need some time to understand the best wardrobe size for your space? Hope our blog on <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/wardrobe-dimensions\/\">wardrobe dimensions<\/a> makes it easier for you. That\u2019s not all \u2014 you can also explore our blog section for wardrobe designs in other shades and get them customised in black, just like you want it.<\/p>\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fieldset class=\"field-set\">\n<!-- <legend align=\"left\"> -->\n                    \n    <h3 class=\"widget-title text-dark text-center mb-0\">Unwind In Your Personal Sanctuary<\/h3>\n  \n \n     <p class=\"text-center text-dark mt-0\"> Get 20% extra space with modular interiors<\/p>\n    <!-- <\/legend> -->\n<form id=\"blogContactUsFormMain\" action=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/get_quote_action.php\" method=\"post\"\n    novalidate=\"novalidate\">\n    <div class=\"form-group\">\n        <input type=\"text\" class=\"form-control\"  name=\"your-name\" placeholder=\"Enter your name*\" \/>\n        <!-- <span class=\"sales-txt-label\" id=\"labeltxt\">Enter your name*<\/span>  -->\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"form-row dc-falg-row\">\n        <!-- <div class=\"form-group col-md-3 guideForm\">\n            <select name=\"your-phone-ext\" id=\"id_select2_example\" class=\"id_select2_example drop-downfield form-dropdown\"\n                onfocus='this.size=5;' onblur='this.size=1;' onchange='this.size=1; this.blur();'\n                data-width=\"100%\" data-minimum-results-for-search=\"Infinity\">\n               \n                <option value=\"+01\"\n                    data-img_src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/06163948\/01.png\